The paper is about distributed machine learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The focus of the paper is on the impact of staleness on the convergence of ML algorithms in distributed environments. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
